283
00:25:15,080 --> 00:25:20,760
complicated an issue teaching English and 
elementary schools is and how much effort it takes

284
00:25:21,560 --> 00:25:29,480
from ALTs, teachers and the Board of Education 
to make the most of limited class time and resources 
and help students get the most out of that effort.

285
00:25:29,720 --> 00:25:35,960
I haven't even touched on many other challenges 
like the language barrier between teachers and ALTs,

286
00:25:36,600 --> 00:25:46,600
differences not only in culture, but personality and 
students with special needs, students to get themselves 
stuck in the I don't speak English category and

287
00:25:47,880 --> 00:25:51,960
students who are very very keen to learn English 
until it comes to speaking.

288
00:25:53,480 --> 00:25:56,680
There is a lot I've left out, but I've tried to be thorough.

289
00:25:57,480 --> 00:25:59,480
I've also tried to be more

290
00:25:59,480 --> 00:26:03,560
constructive than critical and, although 
I've probably missed that mark a few times,

291
